        " قَالَ رَسُولُ اللَّهِ ص طُوبَی لِمَنْ وَجَدَ فِی صَحِیفَتِهِ یَوْمَ الْقِیَامَهِ تَحْتَ کُلِّ ذَنْبٍ أَسْتَغْفِرُ اللَّهَ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "5.  Imam  Muhammad  (a.s.)  narrates  that  the  Holy  Prophet (s.a.w.s.) said, “One who has Astaghfirullaah written under each  of his sin on the Day of Judgment is indeed fortunate.”"
        ]
